title: Zeity Ducks 4/15: Drew Barrymore, Open It Back Up, OBJ, Stimulus Check (PNC)
itunes:title: Zeity Ducks 4/15: Drew Barrymore, Open It Back Up, OBJ, Stimulus Check (PNC)
description:
On this edition of the Zeity Ducks Jack and Miles discuss Drew Barrymore talking about being a parent and business owner in the COVID age, people are out in the streets protesting to get the country back open, Odell Beckham Jr may be traded to the Vikings, and some Stimulus Checks are en route and some are held back by a missing signature.
